== 制作 ==
2012年3月8日，[[麗絲·韋花絲潘|麗絲·韋花絲潘]]表示她所属的制片公司 Pacific Standard 将拍摄[[雪兒·史翠德|雪兒·史翠德]]所写的回忆录《''{{link-en|Wild: From Lost to Found on the Pacific Crest Trail|Wild: From Lost to Found on the Pacific Crest Trail}}''》，并且自己担任主演<ref name="Witherspoon">{{cite web|url=http://www.oregonlive.com/books/index.ssf/2012/03/reese_witherspoon_buys_movie_r.html|title=Reese Witherspoon buys movie rights to Cheryl Strayed's memoir|last=Baker|first=Jeff|work=The Oregonian|date=March 8, 2012|accessdate=August 29, 2014|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426232320/http://www.oregonlive.com/books/index.ssf/2012/03/reese_witherspoon_buys_movie_r.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月，[[福斯探照灯影业|福斯探照灯影业]]取得书籍改编权，并由Nick Hornby改编剧本<ref name="FoxSearchlight">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fox-searchlight-takes-reese-witherspoons-586288|title=Fox Searchlight Takes on Reese Witherspoon's 'Wild'|last=Kilday|first=Gregg|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=July 16, 2013|accessdate=August 29, 2014|archive-date=2020-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111025929/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fox-searchlight-takes-reese-witherspoons-586288|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年8月，让-马克·瓦雷确认执导<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/08/dallas-buyers-club-helmer-jean-marc-vallee-goes-wild-with-reese-witherspoon-569188/|title=‘Dallas Buyers Club’ Helmer Jean-Marc Vallée Goes ‘Wild’ With Reese Witherspoon|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Michael|publisher=Deadline.com|date=August 21, 2013|accessdate=August 29, 2014|archive-date=2020-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205041145/https://deadline.com/2013/08/dallas-buyers-club-helmer-jean-marc-vallee-goes-wild-with-reese-witherspoon-569188/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年10月11日影片开拍，取景地位于[[加州|加州]]和[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]]<ref name="ProductionStart">{{cite web|title=Production Begins on Wild, Starring Reese Witherspoon|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=110075|accessdate=October 15, 2013|publisher=ComingSoon|date=October 11, 2013|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018005955/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=110075|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]网站221个专业影评新鲜度为90%。[[MetaCritic|MetaCritic]]上45家媒体综评76分。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》给88分：就主演威瑟斯彭而言，她隐藏了她“美国甜心”的形象。她几乎毫无装饰，带来了具有勇气的表演。Film.com给80分：影片真诚而又令人难以忘怀，而且给人以共鸣。导演出色，剧本灵巧，表演勇敢<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/12/08/1534942-3.html#content |title=《饥饿游戏3》北美三连冠 |access-date=2014-12-08 |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725081046/http://news.mtime.com/2014/12/08/1534942-3.html#content |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

